{"tid":1364913,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"週末單車遊新界：元朗/天水圍/下白泥單車路徑推介","createTime":"2019-07-25T13:01:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T13:04:56.000Z","uid":68080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f43da9cdb74cfac53a2413bf8befdcb8735090ec","tid":1364913,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"原來新界有咁多地方踩單車遊覽，大家週末無野做真係可以踩單車周圍去認識香港美麗風光<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天水圍又可以去元朗屏山文物徑；又可以去下白泥，睇完日落就踩去食B仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過大家真係要小心安全，租單車既時候D頭盔護具唔好打算慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要安全第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCredit To:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.skyscanner.com.hk/news/inspiration/5cycling-routes-in-new-territories-201704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.skyscanner.com.hk%2Fnews%2Finspiration%2F5cycling-routes-in-new-territories-201704&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6RZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=6cc26ce5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.skyscanner.com.hk/news/inspiration/5cycling-routes-in-new-territories-201704</a><br />\n<br />\nBtw有無天水圍人可以話我知邊度租單車最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd0b7b8b59b7afd76925abbb8b6eb1621250bdf","tid":1364913,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:04:56.000Z","msg":"仲諗緊出唔出元朗好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}